data.description: Disruption break is crazy good on this gl and when paired with an smg or sidearm for hot swapping makes this gl one of the best weapons in the game for almost any scenario.

Chill clip is able to do more damage than explosive light/lasting impression when used with gjallarhorn.
https://dm.reddit.com/r/DestinyTheGame/comments/uta9jo/palmyrad_with_chill_clip_will_do_more_damage_than/
Only put adagio as pvp godroll because the radiant buff allows it to one shot body.

Opening shot passively grants 25 range. Corkscrew grants +5 range/handling/stability which is just enough to bring the range to 100(with either accurized rounds or range masterwork) while also benefiting stability and handling. If you pair fluted barrel/accurized rounds with a handling masterwork and opening shot you can hit 100 handling and range at the cost of your rate of fire.
